'''Brine Phantom''' is a {{Rarity|Legendary}} fish found in the [[Desolate Deep]]'s [[Desolate Deep#Brine Pool|Brine Pool]].

== Description ==
{{Description|The Brine Phantom is a hostile predator of the Desolate Deep Brine Pool. They possess several sharp mandibles on the front of their face, which they use to subdue prey. The Brine Phantom inhibits aggressive behaviour towards other creatures that happen to come anywhere close to it.|Bestiary Entry}}

